      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">What is the primary purpose of using Triple Sugar Iron (TSI) agar in microbiological cultures?</span></span></span></span></p>",
